
.. _object_OpcUaNS0:


:index:`OpcUaNS0`
-----------------

Description
***********

The OpcUaNS0 object provides constants for all node ID types from the `OPC UA namespace 0 <https://files.opcfoundation.org/schemas/UA/1.04/Opc.Ua.NodeIds.csv>`_

This object was introduced in InCore 2.4.
